<item>
            <title>[LU-19210] aarch64 sanity test_130i: dev # 0000: 1020 != 512</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19210</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Marc Vef &amp;lt;mvef@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ae7ee2f7-1b18-43e3-ae54-37c5b42668aa&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ae7ee2f7-1b18-43e3-ae54-37c5b42668aa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_130i failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 130i: FIEMAP (DoM file) =================== 09:35:07 (1758533707)
Filesystem type is: bd00bd0
File size of /mnt/lustre/f130i.sanity is 3141632 (3068 blocks of 1024 bytes)
 ext:     device_logical:        physical_offset: length:  dev: flags:
   0:        0..    1019:    1114176..   1115195:   1020: 0000: merged,net
   1:      512..    1531:     680320..    681339:   1020: 0001: net
   2:      512..    1531:     684032..    685051:   1020: 0000: last,net
/mnt/lustre/f130i.sanity: 3 extents found

sanity test_130i: @@@@@@ FAIL: dev # 0000: 1020 != 512
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/24571&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/24571&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-503.40.1.el9_5.aarch64+64k&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/24571&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es-reviews/24571&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-503.40.1_lustre.ddn1.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Either an issue with the subtest assuming some on-disk blocksize based on 4KiB patches, or FIEMAP mapping and the Lustre ioctl handling issues with large pages.&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_130i - dev # 0000: 1020 != 512&lt;/p&gt;</description>
